> Does  someone  have  any  docs and examples for the "CrmDecrunch"
> Command? Maybe you can help me...

I've never used it specifically,but there are docs for it in the 'BB2 library
guide v1.3'.I've attached the page on CrMDecrunch.

Here's roughly how I would use it on a compressed bitmap:

---
 Size.l=Peek.l(?INCBINLABEL+6) ;size of unpacked file - see file header.

 add.l=Allocmem(Size.l,#CHIP|#CLEAR)

 CrMDecrunch ?INCBINLABEL,add.l

 Cludgebitmap 0,width,height,depth,add.l


INCBINLABEL:
 IncBin "crmfile.crm"
---

